.TH "nvme_init_identify_ns" 9 "nvme_init_identify_ns" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_identify_ns \- Initialize passthru command for NVMe Identify Namespace data structure
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_identify_ns
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u32 nsid "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_id_ns *id "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Command data structure to initialize
.IP "nsid" 12
Namespace identifier
.IP "id" 12
User space destination address to transfer the data
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Identify command with
CNS value NVME_IDENTIFY_CNS_NS.
